---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTAButton from "@/components/CTAButton.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="1West SBA is a small-business lending team focused exclusively on SBA 7(a) financing."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brand">
      About 1West SBA
    </h1>
    <div class="prose prose-slate mt-8 max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">
        1West SBA is dedicated to one thing: helping small businesses secure SBA
        7(a) financing. We pair a modern, streamlined application with
        experienced underwriters and loan officers who understand the program
        inside and out.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-slate-700">
        The SBA 7(a) loan program is the Small Business Administration's primary
        financing vehicle, offering up to $5 million for working capital,
        equipment, commercial real estate, debt refinancing, and business
        acquisition. We help you navigate eligibility, documentation, and the
        approval process from start to finish.
      </p>
      <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-brand">Our approach</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-700">
        <li>
          <strong>Transparent.</strong> No black-box scoring. A real underwriter reviews every file.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Responsive.</strong> One dedicated loan officer from application to funding.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Focused.</strong> SBA 7(a) is all we do, so we do it well.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <CTAButton href="/contact">Talk to a loan officer</CTAButton>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
